sequenceDiagram
    title: New Note on Single Page App

    Note over Browser:
        When the form button is pressed,
        the browser transmits the user input to the server.
        The Content-Type header specifies
        that the data format is JSON.
    end note

    Browser->>Server: HTTP POST 	https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa

    Note over Server:
        The server responds with status code 201 Created.
        Unlike before, it does not request a redirect.
        The browser stays on the same page,
        and no further HTTP requests are made.
    end note

    Server-->>Browser: Responds with HTTP status code 201

    Note over Browser:
        The browser does NOT reload the Notes page.
    end note


